Class DataWriteQueue

java.lang.Object
  de.Lathanael.BinaryFileDB.BaseClass.DataWriteQueue

public class DataWriteQueue
extends java.lang.Object

Implements a simple Queue to lesser the IO of the harddisk by reducing write accesses.

Author:
Lathanael (aka Philippe Leipold)
